
---

### 12. `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# R
.Rproj.user
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata
renv/library/
renv/staging/
renv/.renv

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.env
venv/
.venv/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Portfolio specific (optional)
assets/videos/*.mp4  # uncomment if video files are large
assets/docs/*.pdf     # uncomment if PDFs are private
.positai
